; Single style + single dialogue. The sub line is styled inline (smaller, non-bold,
; Montserrat Medium) so both lines share ONE continuous opaque green box instead
; of rendering as two disconnected boxes.
;
; BorderStyle 4 = opaque box. OutlineColour set to the same neon green as BackColour
; so the "outline" effectively acts as padding that extends the green fill around
; the text without drawing any visible letter stroke.
; Alignment 8 = top-center. MarginV is pixels from the top edge.

